    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well cared for, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean interior that makes every commute enjoyable. It's a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today!",
