    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a lower price point. The engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some minor vibrations at high speeds and the suspension is starting to show its age. Externally, there are several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. The interior shows moderate wear, including a few small tears in the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. It has been regularly serviced, but it will likely require some minor mechanical attention, such as new brake pads and a tune-up, in the near future. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle preserved in showroom-original state. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior, reflecting a standard of maintenance that borders on the obsessive. Every component has been meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for mechanical and aesthetic excellence. This is, without compromise, the finest example of its kind currently available on the market.",
      "price": 46500.0,
